                " \n \n \n \nSHEQ OFFICER GLOBAL GRADE 09\nBoksburg BRC, ZA\nFull-Time\nBRC\nSHEQ Officer Global Grade 09\nApply To Position\nApply Using LinkedIn\n \nKey Outputs\nEnsuring a safe and healthy working environment that complies with current health and safety legislation for all Barloworld Equipment employees\nEnsure all Barloworld Equipment employees in area of responsibility fully understand the requirements of existing health and safety legislation\nInvestigate and report on all work-related injuries and vehicle road accidents\nAssist in HIRA,SOP,PTO, etc, Maintain/control contamination standards for area of responsibility.\nAudit relevant Barloworld Equipment sections and prepare the Willis Blue, ISO 9001, ISO 14001, and ISO 45001, CC Audits\nConduct regular on-site appraisals of premises and housekeeping, electrical, mechanical, and personal safeguards, fire protection and security standards\nFeedback on performance of SHEQ management system to SHEQ manager\nRecommend corrective actions for non-conformances identified during internal audits/inspections and verify implementation\nParticipate in internal and external SHEQ Audits (Internal auditor) \u2022 Do general administration functions and ensure record keeping is up to standard\nDo general administration functions and ensure record keeping is up to standard\nMaintain an effective Tools Calibration program\n \nQualification, Experience and Competencies\nGrade 12 with a technical background\nAt least 2 years\u2019 experience in health and safety management, Projects\u2019 BBS problem solving\nNational Diploma in SHEQ management or equivalent will be an advantage\nTrade certificate will be an advantage\nSound knowledge of health and safety legislation and occupational health and safety requirements\nSAMTRAC, COMSOC 1, COMSOC 2 Certification or \u00e9quivalent certification\nComputer literate (Sound knowledge of MS Office) and Driver\u2019s License \u2013 Code B\nAnalytical Ability; Rule Orientation; Assertiveness; Influencing and Negotiation Judgement and decision making\nISO9001:2015 Implementation and Auditing\nContamination Control Implementation and Auditing Experience will be an advantage\nISO45001 Implementation and Auditing\nEffective verbal and written communication skills, Investigative orientation; Effective\n \n \n \n ",
